    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the CFD hemolysis prediction package for the VAD COU. The model demonstrated generally satisfactory agreement with available bench test data, and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed for hemolysis model constants. Seven factors were assessed and the overall body of evidence was judged sufficient to support regulatory submission. The team determined that the model is fit for purpose for predicting hemolysis trends in the VAD operating envelope and the package is accepted.",
